name: Extensions
body:
### Welcome to My Extensions.
The code is freely available at [Github](https://github.com/ruskindantra/extensions).

### Designer Templates
Weâ€™ve crafted some handsome templates for you to use. Go ahead and click 'Continue to layouts' to browse through them. You can easily go back to edit your page before publishing. After publishing your page, you can revisit the page generator and switch to another theme. Your Page content will be preserved.

### Type Extensions
1. AllImplementors
2. HasInterface<TInterface>
3. GetInterface<TInterface>
4. GetBaseTypes

### Object Extensions
1. SerializeToXml<T>
2. DeserializeFromXml<T>
3. ThrowIfNull<T>

### Byte Extensions
1. AsByteString

### Data Structures
1. XmlSerializableInterfaceList<T>

### Authors and Contributors
If you would like to see any custom extensions added to this library or to report a bug please contain @ruskindantra.
